name: s_m_load_msgr_facts_pms_new_vw4
description: Session pushed from PC to ICS : s_m_load_msgr_facts_pms_new_vw4

parameters.name: $SQ_PMS_Fact_Loss$
parameters.label: DBConnection_SRC
parameters.customQuery:
SELECT PMS_Fact_Loss.Policy_Key_Code,
PMS_Fact_Loss.Policy_Key,
PMS_Fact_Loss.Claim_Key,
PMS_Fact_Loss.Major_Peril_ID,
PMS_Fact_Loss.Risk_State_ID,
PMS_Fact_Loss.Loss_Cause,
PMS_Fact_Loss.Loss_Cause_Desc,
PMS_Fact_Loss.StateLine,
PMS_Fact_Loss.Account_Entered_Dt,
PMS_Fact_Loss.Accident_Dt,
PMS_Fact_Loss.Reported_Dt,
PMS_Fact_Loss.Claim_Type,
PMS_Fact_Loss.Loss_Adjustor_No,
PMS_Fact_Loss.Loss_Paid_Amt,
PMS_Fact_Loss.Loss_Paid_Recovery_Amt,
PMS_Fact_Loss.Loss_Salvage,
PMS_Fact_Loss.Loss_Subrogation_Amt,
PMS_Fact_Loss.Loss_Ulae_Expense,
PMS_Fact_Loss.Loss_Alae_Expense,
PMS_Fact_Loss.Loss_Reserve_Amt,
PMS_Fact_Loss.Loss_Reserve_For_Incurred_Loss,
PMS_Fact_Loss.Transaction_CD,
PMS_Fact_Loss.Transaction_Dt,
PMS_Fact_Loss.annual_statement_line,
TGT.row_id,
TGT.md5_hash_value
FROM
 dbo.PMS_Fact_Loss
left join dbo.msgr_facts_pms_new_vw4 TGT on
	PMS_Fact_Loss.Policy_Key = TGT.Policy_Key AND
	PMS_Fact_Loss.Policy_Key_Code = TGT.Policy_Key_Code AND
	PMS_Fact_Loss.Major_Peril_ID = TGT.Major_Peril_ID AND
	PMS_Fact_Loss.Risk_State_ID = TGT.Risk_State_ID AND
	PMS_Fact_Loss.Account_Entered_Dt = TGT.Account_Entered_Dt AND
	NVL(PMS_Fact_Loss.StateLine,'NA') = NVL(TGT.StateLine,'NA') AND
	NVL(PMS_Fact_Loss.annual_statement_line,'NA') = NVL(TGT.annual_statement_line,'NA')
where date_part(YEAR, PMS_Fact_Loss.Account_Entered_Dt) >= 2008 and 
--PMS_Fact_Loss.Account_Entered_Dt >=dateadd(month, -1, cast(getdate() as date))
insert_date>= (SELECT etlbatchstartst FROM dbo.loadbatchetldt WHERE loadetltype = 'wf_msgr_views')
ORDER BY
PMS_Fact_Loss.Policy_Key_Code,
PMS_Fact_Loss.Policy_Key,
PMS_Fact_Loss.Claim_Key,
PMS_Fact_Loss.Major_Peril_ID,
PMS_Fact_Loss.Risk_State_ID,
PMS_Fact_Loss.Loss_Cause,
PMS_Fact_Loss.Loss_Cause_Desc,
PMS_Fact_Loss.StateLine,
PMS_Fact_Loss.Account_Entered_Dt,
PMS_Fact_Loss.Accident_Dt,
PMS_Fact_Loss.Reported_Dt,
PMS_Fact_Loss.Claim_Type,
PMS_Fact_Loss.Loss_Adjustor_No,
PMS_Fact_Loss.Transaction_CD,
PMS_Fact_Loss.Transaction_Dt,
PMS_Fact_Loss.annual_statement_line,
TGT.row_id,
TGT.md5_hash_value
